🏭 PRODUCTION MODULE — COMPLETE VISUAL FLOW
1️⃣ Tabs Overview (Top Navigation inside “Production”)
──────────────────────────────────────────────
🏭 PRODUCTION
──────────────────────────────────────────────
[ Orders ] [ W.O. ] [ Machines ] [ QC ] [ Ready ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Default = Orders (Supervisor) or Machines (Operator)

Tabs scroll horizontally if needed

Each tab = role-specific stage in production

2️⃣ ORDERS TAB (Supervisor – SO-level view)

Purpose: See confirmed Sales Orders, start production, monitor progress.

