Product: Grey Fabric   | Qty: 1200m
Material: ✅ Available
Status: 🔵 In Production
Progress: █████░░░░ 60%
[ View Work Orders ▾ ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
▼ Expand WOs (optional)
  - WO#2347-A  Loom A1 | 400m | Done ✅
  - WO#2347-B  Loom A2 | 300m | Running 🟡
  - WO#2347-C  Loom A3 | 500m | Not Started 🔴
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Actions:

Start Production → Creates WOs (auto-breakdown), reserves stock, moves to W.O. tab

Go to Procurement → jumps to procurement module

View Work Orders → expand inline or go to W.O. tab

3️⃣ W.O. TAB (Planner / Supervisor – WO-level view)

Purpose: Manage all work orders across machines.

──────────────────────────────────────────────
🗂 WORK ORDERS   [Filter: All ▾]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
WO#2345-A  SO#2345 Ajay Textiles
Machine: Loom A1  | Worker: Vikram
Planned: 400m  | Done: 400m ✅ Completed
[ View WO ]  [ History ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
WO#2345-B  SO#2345 Ajay Textiles
Machine: Loom A2  | Worker: Priya
Planned: 600m  | Done: 300m 🟡 Running
[ + Update Qty ] [ Reassign Machine ] [ View WO ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
WO#2346-A  SO#2346 Bharat Mills
Machine: Loom B1 | Worker: — 
Planned: 500m | Done: 0m 🔴 Not Started
[ Assign Machine ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Actions:

+ Update Qty → enter progress popup

Reassign Machine → pick from available machines

Assign Machine → assign WO to a machine/worker

View WO → opens WO Detail screen

