Scrap: [ 5 ] m
Notes: [ Optional ]
[ Save Progress ]

4️⃣ MACHINES TAB (Operator view – machine-level execution)

Purpose: Operator runs, updates, and completes WOs on their assigned machine.

──────────────────────────────────────────────
🏭 MACHINES
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Loom A2 (Priya)  |  Status: 🟡 Running
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Current WO: WO#2345-B — Ajay Textiles
Qty: 600m | Produced: 300m | Remaining: 300m
[ Start WO ]  [ + Update Qty ]  [ Pause ]  [ Mark Complete ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Next in Queue:
- WO#2348-A  | Ajay Textiles  | 0/400 🔴
- WO#2349-A  | Bharat Mills   | 0/300 🔴
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Operator Flow:

Tap Start WO when run begins → WO status → Running

Tap + Update Qty to record daily/shift progress

Tap Pause if stopped due to issue

Tap Mark Complete when done → triggers QC entry

Notes:

Operators see only their machine(s) and assigned WOs

Supervisor sees all machines + operator names

5️⃣ QC TAB (QC Inspector / Supervisor)

Purpose: Inspect completed WOs, record quality status.

──────────────────────────────────────────────
🔎 QC QUEUE
──────────────────────────────────────────────
WO#2345-B — Ajay Textiles | Loom A2
Qty: 600m | Completed: 22 Dec | Pending QC
[ Start QC ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
QC FORM:
Color match: [✓]  GSM: [✓]  Defects: [0]
Photo: [📷 Capture]
Remarks: ________________________
Result:  [ ✅ Pass ]   [ ⚠️ Rework ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Actions:

Pass → WO status = Completed (QC passed)

Rework → system creates new WO (WO#2345-B-R1), sends to W.O. tab

Once all WOs under SO pass QC → SO moves to “Ready” tab

6️⃣ READY TAB (Dispatch / Store view)

Purpose: Manage packing, dispatch, and invoicing for Sales Orders ready for shipment.

──────────────────────────────────────────────
📦 READY FOR DISPATCH
──────────────────────────────────────────────
SO#2345 Ajay Textiles
Product: Cotton Fabric | Qty: 1000m
All Work Orders QC Passed ✅
Ready Since: 23 Dec 10:00 AM
[ Pack & Dispatch ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Pack & Dispatch Form
──────────────────────────────────────────────
