Driver:  [ Suresh Patel ▾ ]
Invoice: Auto-generated (INV-00123)
Notify Customer: [WhatsApp ✓] [SMS ✓]
[ Confirm Dispatch ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Actions:

Pack & Dispatch → creates Delivery Challan + Invoice, marks SO → Dispatched

Dispatch details go to Sales / Invoice / Payments module

7️⃣ ROLE-BASED NAVIGATION SUMMARY
Role	Default Tab	Visible Tabs	Typical Actions
Supervisor / Planner	Orders	Orders, W.O., Machines, QC, Ready	Start Production, Assign Machines, Approve QC, Dispatch
Operator	Machines	Machines	Start, Update, Pause, Complete WOs
QC Inspector	QC	QC, Ready	QC Pass/Fail, Rework
Store / Dispatch	Ready	Ready	Pack, Dispatch
Owner	Orders	All	Review progress, oversee dispatch
8️⃣ END-TO-END DATA FLOW (System Summary)
Sales Order (SO)
     │
     ▼
[ ORDERS TAB ]
Supervisor taps → "Start Production"
     │
     ▼
Work Orders (WO) auto-created
     │
     ▼
[ W.O. TAB ]
Plan, assign machines, monitor progress
     │
     ▼
[ MACHINES TAB ]
Operators produce, update, complete
     │
     ▼
[ QC TAB ]
Inspector validates, pass/rework
     │
     ▼
[ READY TAB ]
Dispatch, pack, invoice auto-generated
     │
     ▼
Sales → Payment → Close Order

💡 DESIGN PRINCIPLES IMPLEMENTED
Principle	Implementation
MSME Simplicity	1-tap actions, minimal typing
Visual Consistency	Cards + CTAs + progress bars
Role-based UX	Tabs auto-filtered per user
Mobile-first	Scrollable tabs, 1 column layout
Scalable	Can add Rework, Maintenance, Dashboard later
ERP-compliant	WOs at core, SO linkage preserved
Traceable	QC & Ready separated cleanly

✅ Summary — Production module final layout

🏭 PRODUCTION
──────────────────────────────────────────────
[ Orders ] [ W.O. ] [ Machines ] [ QC ] [ Ready ]
──────────────────────────────────────────────
 Orders → Start Production
 W.O. → Manage and track all work orders
 Machines → Operator runs jobs
 QC → Quality validation
 Ready → Packing & Dispatch
──────────────────────────────────────────────


Every tab has a single purpose,
and all 5 together form the complete real-life production flow for MSMEs.